---
title: Blueberry Beyond Meat® Burgers with Rosemary Potato Coins and Mustard Aioli
description: These Beyond Meat® burgers smothered in blueberry jam, mustard aioli and melty cheddar cheese check all the right flavour boxes! The earthy rosemary roasted potatoes provide a lovely complementary flavour.
